  "detailed_description": "A small, third-person adventure game with action elements and a marvel atmosphere of magic world. The plot is pretty simple - wizard's apprentice attempting to save his teacher from the evil threat and it's up to you to help him on his way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/6c205a54632a66fb53290a7e880a8b96.poster.avif?t=1663867178\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/6c205a54632a66fb53290a7e880a8b96.webm?t=1663867178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/6c205a54632a66fb53290a7e880a8b96.mp4?t=1663867178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cartoon Halloween atmosphere.<br></li><li> Beautiful fabulous game design, as well as sounds and music.<br></li><li> Funny NPCs.<br></li><li> Some light puzzles and platforming.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/097e1dfd7e3bd82b73ae1c4eb88810ee.poster.avif?t=1663867178\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/097e1dfd7e3bd82b73ae1c4eb88810ee.webm?t=1663867178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/097e1dfd7e3bd82b73ae1c4eb88810ee.mp4?t=1663867178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Lots of hidden treasures.<br></li><li> Learning a new spells/upgrades by collecting Magic Tomes.<br></li><li> Collect as many gold coins as possible to get higher scores.<br></li><li> Spend coins on Healing Potions and Life Crystals.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/43eb0c9421f18f5d5f09f5d1dceb5f0f.poster.avif?t=1663867178\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/43eb0c9421f18f5d5f09f5d1dceb5f0f.webm?t=1663867178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993110/extras/43eb0c9421f18f5d5f09f5d1dceb5f0f.mp4?t=1663867178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
